posts.name: Benjamin Hall
posts.cooked:
You don’t want to modify SwerveModule to construct all the CANcoders and TalonFX devices; each swerve module should only have one CANcoder, one drive TalonFX, and one steer TalonFX. Instead, you should create a public static final String kCANbus = "Canivorebus"; in the Constants file’s Swerve class and modify the device constructors already in the BaseTalonFXSwerve template to use that Constants.Swerve.kCANbus .

For example:
